The Democracy Youth Round Table Special Online Series which was held Online On democracy day Friday 12th June 2020 attracted huge followership On Instagram Live ,lot of youth bared their mind  on ways to make our Democratic system works better as well as how youth can be part of decision process in Nigeria . There was serious discussion on how the youth have to positioned themselves for leadership in politics, though money is a factor but the youth of Nigeria must believe in themselves that they can do it ,also we deliberated on the need for government to include youth into position of authority because we are the hope of the Nation and the need for government to introduce Electronic voting System to our electoral process to help the menace of election malpractice. The Event attracted top class guests like Media Guru Bashorun Dele Momodu Chairman Ovation International, Hon Kabir ibrahim Tukura a member of house of Representatives from Kebbi State ,Hon Bimbo Daramola, CEO One United Africa, Mr Ahmed Buhari, Amb Ndubuisi Nzenweofor, Mr Dayo lsreal, Mrs Bunmi Ademosu, Special adviser to Ondo State Governor on Inter Governmental Relations, as well as Amb UTCHAY Odims, Mr Vin Martin Ilo, Mr Hamzat Lawal and Nollywood Veteran Mr Emeka Ike  to mention a few. The Special Online Series was anchored by Amb Demond Agboola Executive Director Democracy Youth Round Table and Deletable Miss Ogenna Ekwubiri CEO Motivating Africa Youth Initiative. 